<h4 id="rspec">RSpec</h4>
<p><a href="http://rspec.info/" target="_blank">The RSpec ruby gem</a> is useful and has an intuitive syntax to test your Rails or plain Ruby code. Itâ€™s essential for Test Driven Development with Ruby.<br /></p>

<center><img src="/assets/images/bug.svg" /></center>

<h4 id="byebug">Byebug</h4>
<p><a href="https://github.com/deivid-rodriguez/byebug" target="_blank">Byebug </a>is a great debugger for Ruby that can help you find whatâ€™s preventing your code from working the way it should be.<br /></p>

